    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHILDREN OF SATURN</strong> blends first person adventure gameplay with real video recordings to tell an authentic slice of life story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120360/extras/75496e2f3506e80ae9073d5f586ea328.poster.avif?t=1736530761\" width=616 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120360/extras/75496e2f3506e80ae9073d5f586ea328.webm?t=1736530761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120360/extras/75496e2f3506e80ae9073d5f586ea328.mp4?t=1736530761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the lens of a VHS camera, experience some of the most significant moments in the lives of a group of friends growing up in a time of absolute hopelessness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suburban exploration (aka trespassing) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Home parties </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teen angst </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skating </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loitering with friends </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listening to mixtapes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wasting your youth (again) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vandalism </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Theft </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mundanity </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120360/extras/b95c3afd50f5f9bd87a12c7378706c4d.poster.avif?t=1736530761\" width=616 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120360/extras/b95c3afd50f5f9bd87a12c7378706c4d.webm?t=1736530761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120360/extras/b95c3afd50f5f9bd87a12c7378706c4d.mp4?t=1736530761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to find hope under an orange sky.</p>",
